quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"Simoore, Min njippinii nde Min farlii nde, Min njippini e ndeer mayre aayeeje …ďanngu…óe mbelejo'o onon on mbaajitoto."
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jinoowo on foccee gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe paatawol(looci) teemedere, wota njurmeende ma…ď…ďe nanngu on e fii Diina Alla ka, si tawii on laatike ho…óon ngooŇč…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol …ďe ngol jamaa immorde e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jonoowo maa…óum cirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resata mo si wonaa gorko jinoowo ma cirkoowo, …óum harminaama e dow gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  24,4,"E …ďen …ďe no tukka rew…ďe saŇčii…ďe …ďen refti …ďe ngaddaani seedee…ďe nayo, piyee …ďe paatawol(lo'oci) cappan…óe jeetati. Wota on nja…ďan …ďe ceedagol poomaa. ∆Āen …óon, ko kam…ďe ngoni Faasiqii…ďe …ďen."
  24,5,"Si wonaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óuum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko O cuhroowo jurmetee…óo."
  24,6,"E …ďeen …ďe no tukka sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen hara laatanaaki …ďe seedee…ďe si wonaa wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko yo go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kako ko e googu…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  24,7,"Jowa…ďun …óum, won'dema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ďe …ďeen."
  24,8,"∆Āe ndu√Īira e [sonnaajo on] lepte …óen, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenoo…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  24,9,"Jowa…ďum …óum, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e gooŇču…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  24,10,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonan'dema Alla ko O ja…ďoowo tuubuubuye √Ďee√Ī…óo."